all the natural surroundings.

00:09:06.891 --> 00:09:08.440
So we created an
observatory, which

00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:12.230
is a place where you can,
well, observe what's going on

00:09:12.230 --> 00:09:15.400
and try and make sense of what
a rather complex system is

00:09:15.400 --> 00:09:18.220
the intersections perhaps
of natural and human

00:09:18.220 --> 00:09:20.190
made phenomenon.

00:09:20.190 --> 00:09:22.340
We also have a large
outdoor campus.

00:09:22.340 --> 00:09:23.940
Outdoor exhibits
are not new to us.

00:09:23.940 --> 00:09:26.570
But to have space
on our own campus

00:09:26.570 --> 00:09:28.620
where we can be exploring
outdoor surroundings

00:09:28.620 --> 00:09:31.260
was a wonderful opportunity
of the new building.

00:09:31.260 --> 00:09:33.530
So we began creating
experiences outside.

00:09:33.530 --> 00:09:35.380
This is an anamorphic bench.

00:09:35.380 --> 00:09:38.200
