looked in a curved surface.

00:09:41.520 --> 00:09:43.420
So we reversed it and
put the mutated image

00:09:43.420 --> 00:09:44.260
in the real world.

00:09:44.260 --> 00:09:48.110
And if you look on the cylinder,
you see a rectangular bench.

00:09:48.110 --> 00:09:49.860
We created a mobile
camera obscura.

00:09:49.860 --> 00:09:52.080
There are rickshaws going
up and down the Embarcadero

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:53.370
