it's an incredible time.

00:42:30.340 --> 00:42:33.650
I mean, anybody who's been a
participant the Maker Movement

00:42:33.650 --> 00:42:37.750
or education, whether
it's formal or informal,

00:42:37.750 --> 00:42:40.530
