00:42:47.900 --> 00:42:50.150
perspective, there's
ways in which countries

00:42:50.150 --> 00:42:53.200
can work together as
never before, it's just

00:42:53.200 --> 00:42:55.930
an extraordinary time.

00:42:55.930 --> 00:43:00.284
It's going to be fun to learn
over the next 10, 15, 20 years.

